postReview.title: Nottingham Forest 0-0 Wolves: el equipo de Dyche se atasca con un empate en el City Ground
postReview.description: Nottingham Forest dejó escapar una buena ocasión para tomar aire en la lucha por el descenso en la Premier League al no encontrar la forma de batir al Wolves.

postReview.title: Nottingham Forest 0-0 Wolves: Dyche's side frustrated in City Ground draw
postReview.description: Nottingham Forest missed the chance to pull clear of the Premier League relegation zone after failing to find a way past Wolves.

postReview.title: Nottingham Forest 0-0 Wolves: la squadra di Dyche si ferma sul pari al City Ground
postReview.description: Il Nottingham Forest ha mancato l’occasione di allontanarsi dalla zona retrocessione in Premier League, senza trovare il varco contro il Wolves.

postReview.title: Nottingham Forest 0-0 Wolves: time de Dyche se frustra e empata no City Ground
postReview.description: O Nottingham Forest perdeu a chance de se afastar da zona de rebaixamento da Premier League ao não conseguir furar o bloqueio do Wolves.

postReview.title: Nottingham Forest 0-0 Wolves : le Forest de Dyche frustré au City Ground
postReview.description: Nottingham Forest a manqué l'occasion de prendre ses distances avec la zone de relégation en Premier League, incapable de trouver l'ouverture face à Wolves.

postReview.title: Nottingham Forest 0-0 Wolves: Dyches Team verzweifelt beim Remis im City Ground
postReview.description: Nottingham Forest verpasste die Chance, sich in der Premier League von der Abstiegszone abzusetzen, weil gegen Wolves kein Durchkommen war.

postReview.title: Nottingham Forest 0-0 Wolves: equipa de Dyche frustrada em empate no City Ground
